SESSION.DESCRIPTION: Session will insert the staged data in Global Vendor Spend table
SESSION.NAME: s_m_GVS_DATA_LD

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DELETE gvs FROM sc_procurement.dbo.global_Vendor_Spend AS gvs JOIN sc_procurement.dbo.stg_global_Vendor_Spend AS sgvs ON gvs.source_erp_system = sgvs.source_erp_system AND gvs.pmt_date = sgvs.pmt_date WHERE sgvs.processed_flag = 'N';

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
BEGIN
DECLARE @SESSSTARTTIME datetime
SELECT @SESSSTARTTIME = MAX(Create_Date_Timestamp) FROM dbo.Global_Vendor_Spend
UPDATE dbo.STG_Global_Vendor_Spend SET Processed_Flag = 'Y', Processed_Timestamp = @SESSSTARTTIME, Processed_userid = 'ETL_GVSP_STG_TO_FACT_LD' WHERE Processed_Flag = 'N'
END;
